{"tid":1660844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"線索：popo 27/9喺調景嶺海邊搵乜呢？","createTime":"2019-10-17T18:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T18:27:26.000Z","uid":319195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9381a46ab9d2d601418df8e8bd90dfedc7df8ce6","tid":1660844,"uid":319195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"話說fb將軍澳主場既谷，有條友喺27/9晏晝出post話一班狗喺調景嶺釣魚台附近波堤唔知搵乜。<br />\n<br />\n有其他谷友回應時有提供其他popo搵嘢相，亦有谷友有片影住直升機喺晏晝4點幾喺高空固定咗好似搵乜咁。同post又有人話早兩三日有狗快艇在附近係咁兜圈。<br />\n<br />\n琴日在fb見有聲稱識那位阿媽的人踢爆，阿媽其實29/9先去認屍。<br />\n<br />\n唔知件事有無關呢？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvGRdJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvGRdJb.jpg&h=7412f2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHUzbuS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHUzbuS.jpg&h=4d294bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2eLh9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2eLh9T.jpg&h=88b06914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHVbdJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHVbdJf.jpg&h=fd28ccfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZFq2BB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZFq2BB.jpg&h=fb6164c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycbYC9Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycbYC9Y.jpg&h=d8527dbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22f662a517b5f7ea3575cda7e209e84212038e70","tid":1660844,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"新線索 網媒丘品創作：919當晚全程在海濱做直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n慢慢將啲資料整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37928f749d825b3f134100409c0ffb800d7414